West and South Towns St. R. R. Co. v. Edward B. McKey, Receiver, etc.Appeal from the Circuit Court of Cook County.Opinion filed February 9, 1899.Lyman M. Paine, attorney for appellant.Newman, Northrup & Levinson, attorneys for appellee.

This case was affirmed because no exception to the entry of judgment appeared in the abstract, upon authority of Gribler v. City of Mattoon, 167 Ill. 18, and R. R. Co. v. O’Keefe, 154 Ill. 510, and other cases cited in opinion.
